data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 3-bedroom residence that seamlessly combines modern elegance with practical living. Step inside to discover a traditional layout that's perfect for both daily life and entertaining. The formal living and dining area is suited to meet your formal entertainment needs, while the den and breakfast area are ready to host day to day living. Retreat to one of the three spacious bedrooms, each designed with your comfort in mind. The master suite boasts a luxurious en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet, while the additional bedrooms offer ample space for family or guests. Located just outside of Beltway 8, I-0, and Hwy 6 you will find 16974 Cairntosh. Schedule a viewing today!
